text: Fabio Bonacina (26 July 1923 - March 2012) was an Italian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1923 births Category:2012 deaths Category:Italian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Italy Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:People from Lecco
